        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知侯爷驾到，未曾远迎，多有得罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。末将来的鲁莽，老大王海涵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侯爷到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了汉天子之命，相邀老大王，年年进贡，每岁来朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情愿年年进贡，每岁来朝。请至馆驿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了。\n带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（班超下。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "匈奴国王驾到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（匈奴王上。报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告坐。适才何人到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "班侯爷到来，催讨贡俸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大王怎样回答？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情愿年年进贡，每岁来朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人现在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在馆驿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟有计在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何妙计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今晚三更时分，将馆驿团团围住，将班超杀死，以免我等数载贡俸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计甚好。御弟前行，孤家大兵，随后接应。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，抬枪带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
