    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "匈奴王",
        "班超",
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（班超、四大将同上。〖急急风〗。会阵。四番将、匈奴王同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马前敢是达里呵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带领人马前来则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "匈奴王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。想我西凉各国，哪有贡献与你！特地前来，与你见个高下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好反复无常的匹夫，放马过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（班超、匈奴王同开打，同下，同上。匈奴王接，四大将同下。班超杀匈奴王下。鄯善王上，跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大王，还有何话讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鄯善王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情愿年年进贡，岁岁来朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鄯善王下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "班超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，回朝缴旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖尾声〗。）"
        }
      ],
